===Awards===

* [[Fishbein Trophy]] (1) 1956
* von Zedtwitz Award 2003 <ref>[http://www.fpabridge.org/vonzedtwitz.htm Foundation for the Preservation and Advancement of Bridge - von Zedtwitz Award]</ref>

